1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
A shy lantern blinked three times from
behind a tree near a tiny penguin.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,000
In the seaside dune, the penguin learned that a cloud
had misplaced the silver bell that guided it home.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:13,000
What began as a rescue mission grew harder
when the paper star slipped out of reach.

4
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:17,000
The thoughtful penguin decided to reach the stranded friend and
followed the clues and arranged bright stones into an arrow.

5
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:21,000
The plan worked, bringing a safe rescue
for everyone in the seaside dune.

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:25,000
The new friends celebrated with a tiny dance under the leaves.
The paper star softly echoed the adventure's beginning.
